<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="text-start py-0">
          <p class="accent-text" data-aos="fade-up">Hi, I am </p>
          <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="hero-title">Avis Ejerenwa</h1>
          <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="hero-subtitle">I love to build solutions for the web.</h1>
          <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="hero-caption"> <span class="accent-text">I am, </span> a software
            engineer focused on developing modern web solutions and solving real-world problems with clean code.</p>
          <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-accent-transparent mt-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">View My Work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section id="about" class="container py-5">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
        <div class="col-lg-8 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-uppercase mb-4"><span class="accent-text">01.</span> About Me</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Hello! My name is <span class="fw-bold">Avis Ejerenwa</span>, and I enjoy creating and developing solutions,
            whether it’s improving real-life workflows or building utility applications that supercharge productivity.
            My journey in software development began in 2009, when I learned Core Java to create a stock-keeping application
            for my dad's store.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Fast-forward to today, I’ve had the privilege of working with <span class="accent">Triumph Courier
              Services</span>, a last-mile package delivery service provider in Atlanta, where I developed a full-fledged
            Delivery Dashboard and other productivity-enhancing solutions.
            I also collaborated with <span class="accent">Paris Beauty and Hair Salon</span> to build their website, which
            includes an integrated scheduler for managing appointments and payments.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            I am an <span class="fw-bold">Experienced Software Engineer</span> with a strong background in developing and
            maintaining high-volume, scalable software systems and client-facing web applications.
            I specialize in full stack development, Agile methodologies, and collaborating with cross-functional teams to
            deliver innovative solutions. My focus includes reducing technical debt, improving performance, and keeping up
            with emerging technologies.
          </p>
          <p>
            Here are a few technologies and tools I’ve been working with recently:
          </p>
          <!-- Technologies List -->
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> Java, JavaScript</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> HTML/CSS, Node.js</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> Python</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> SQL, MongoDB, Oracle</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> React, Bootstrap, Express.js</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> REST, JSON, APIs</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> UI/UX Design (Figma, Adobe Suite)</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right accent"></i> Git, GitHub, GitHub Actions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Right Column: Image -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
          <div class="position-relative" style="border: 2px solid #EDA505; border-radius: 5px;">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="Your Image" class="img-fluid rounded">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <div id="projects" class="projects">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">Projects</h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="card project-card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Project One</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Description of Project One. Highlight key features and technologies used.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Details</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="card project-card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Project Two</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Description of Project Two. Highlight key features and technologies used.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Details</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
      <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>

</html>